data.description: Wow, extremely popular plan w/3-car garage ready to pick colors, flooring, granite and tile. This spacious open concept plan features high ceilings, huge windows and Timber Hill Farms style! Finished basement has enormous family room. Large tiled shower with double vanity and large walk-in in Master. The front covered porch is pure Americana. Complete w/access to private fishing lake and walking trail plus an option for additional land to extend back yard, this slice of small-town living won't last long!
data.whatILove: Natural wood floors, 2 living spaces, cathedral ceiling, plenty of natural light
